name: Little Earths: Atlantis
description:
Get yourself a little home under the sea!

There’s so much to explore in the ocean’s depths. So many alien-looking fish species to discover, many sharks to befriend, many missing clownfish to look for. Look for the mermaid/merman of your dreams, make merbabies and start your own little merfamily.

What are you waiting for? Swim by and get your own place in Atlantis!

Not for those with thalassophobia.
